::Ramulus::

Panting like he was about to die of oxygen deprivation, Ramulus bolts into 
the Cybertronian Fire, not slowing down a bit as he runs toward the lab, 
nearly crashing through the door. He runs into the mechanical room, nearly 
crashing into a console as he stops.

"Ok," he says, breathing heavilly, "Now lets do this."

He puts the disk into the console, his fingers flying over the keyboard as he 
begins to enter a programm.
